# .claude/ — track rules (team-shared), ignore agents and settings.local.json
# (agent files and settings.local.json contain machine-specific absolute paths)
.claude/*
!.claude/rules/
.claude/rules/*
!.claude/rules/*.md

# docs/ — planning artifacts stay local
docs/brainstorms/*.md
docs/plans/*.md
docs/solutions/*.md

